An open-source project for real-time interactive streaming digital humans: metahuman-stream, achieving synchronized audio and video dialogue, which can basically reach commercial standards.

1. Supports multiple digital human models;
2. Supports voice cloning;
3. Supports interruption of digital human speech;
4. Supports full-body video stitching;
5. Supports rtmp and webrtc streaming;
6. Supports playing custom videos.

